reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.json:106:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say this is standard raft, upaya, practice-realization, Other Power, spiritual direction, spiritual materialism warning, or ordinary supervision, with no new prediction about repair.",
