reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:59:      "difference": "Lewin centers Eckhart and Heidegger, not Dogen, Shinran, Heart Sutra, or a modern achievement-cohort practice screen.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:65:      "difference": "The candidate turns Shinran into a comparative diagnostic against universal release teachings.",
