reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:67:      "overlap": "Direct primary near-neighbor. Shinran already denies practicer calculation and says no working is true working in Other Power.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:68:      "source": "Shinran, On Jinen-Honi, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:72:      "novelty_impact": "Strong downgrade for the Other Power anomaly and self-power critique.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:73:      "overlap": "Very close. Tannisho says nembutsu is not practice or good act for the practicer because it arises wholly from Other Power and is free of self-power.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:74:      "source": "Tannisho, A Record in Lament of Divergences, https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:83:      "difference": "Pargament studies coping style, not method completion or release of practice results.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:84:      "novelty_impact": "Downgrades agency novelty. The candidate must show voice coding predicts beyond Pargament-style agency coding.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:86:      "source": "Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:109:    "Search and read full Lewin, Pargament, Dogen scholarship, Jodo Shinshu scholarship, grace-effort theology, Gelassenheit, and middle-voice theology before raising novelty.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:111:    "Create a voice-coding sheet with values for active, middle, passive, mixed-by-stage, simultaneous-mixed, no-owner, no-threshold, practice-realization, radical Other Power, analyst-frame-refused, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:114:  "novelty_adjustment": "Lower novelty from 0.55 to 0.39. The strongest prior-art pressure is Lewin's middle-voice analysis plus Shinran's explicit Other Power and Pargament's agency styles. Human-condition fit is strong but narrow: high-striving people with achievement-contingent self-worth, burnout, comparison, and result-ownership. Non-fit cases include acute crisis, severe depression, addiction withdrawal, scrupulosity, dissociation, psychosis, people in grace-centered or nondual practice who do not experience ownership, and people whose distress is caused mainly by structural exploitation rather than self-rating.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:117:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say the claim is simply self-power versus Other Power, grace versus works, practice-realization, or middle-voice theology in new language, and that it does not change sequencing, warning, or repair.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:123:      "Does voice coding change guidance beyond older labels such as self-power, Other Power, grace, surrender, non-attainment, or Pargament coping style?"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:136:      "MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, raft simile, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:137:      "Shinran, On Jinen-Honi and Tannisho, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/ and https://shinranworks.com/related-works-by-other-authors/a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:139:    "risk_of_overread": "High. 'Middle voice' is an analyst metaphor that may not map cleanly onto Japanese, Sanskrit, Pali, or Chinese practice grammar. The active versus middle distinction may become a renamed self-power versus Other Power distinction, or it may hide stage shifts where effort and surrender coexist.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:140:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit did not read Japanese, Pali, Sanskrit, Chinese, or commentarial originals. It did not read full Lewin on middle voice, full Heidegger and Eckhart scholarship, full Pargament, full Hori, full Dogen scholarship, or Jodo Shinshu scholarship beyond accessible translations and summaries. No Shin, Soto, Rinzai, or Christian grace practitioners were interviewed.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:141:    "structural_observation": "MN 22 assumes a practitioner can grasp the Dhamma rightly, use it for crossing, and then not hold it as a possession. Shinran's jinen-honi and Tannisho relocate efficacy to Other Power and repeatedly reject practicer calculation, making even discussion of no working liable to become another working. This is a strong primary-text basis for narrowing release advice by agency grammar. But it also shows the candidate's central insight is not new inside Shinran: one cannot release as self-power what was never self-power to begin with."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-you-cannot-release-what-you-never-held-3f00413ce244b54e.json:153:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Lewin on middle voice, Shinran on Other Power, Dogen on practice-realization, Pargament on religious coping styles, Heart Sutra no-attainment reliance, Smith, Sells, and prior Lumenary completion models, this idea's possible contribution is a testable fit rule: give release-the-method advice only to practitioners whose own language shows active earning and result-ownership, then test whether the advice helps them more than it helps other-power, nondual, or practice-realization practitioners."
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:25:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta raft simile, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html; Heart Sutra no attainment with reliance on prajnaparamita, https://www.fgsitc.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Heart-Sutra-2016.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:26:- Dogen Genjokoan practice-realization, https://brightwayzen.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/For-BWZ-Chant-Book-Genjokoan.pdf; Tannisho sections 6 and 8, Taitetsu Unno translation, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:28:Structural observation: MN 22 is a direct near-neighbor for proper use followed by release, but it also requires right grasp before release. The Heart Sutra denies attainment while retaining reliance and mantra, so undermining a result does not imply abandoning the method. Dogen strains the whole stage-completion frame because practice and realization are not cleanly separable. Tannisho strains practitioner-owned authority because nembutsu is presented as free of self-power and not a good act or practice from the practitioner's side. Together, the primary texts support a scoped coding heuristic, not a discovery-level doctrine.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:30:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors in Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on apophatic unsaying, Pargament agency and coping styles, spiritual materialism, spiritual bypassing, VCE and Cheetah House adverse meditation support, and multiple prior Lumenary audits. Full source reliability still requires reading upaya scholarship, Zen post-kensho training, Shinran scholarship, spiritual direction ethics, and practitioner manuals in original languages where possible.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:38:- "Koan and Kensho" "Rinzai Zen Curriculum" Hori post kensho
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:39:- "Alagaddupama Sutta" raft simile Dhamma for crossing not for retaining
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:40:- Tannisho Other Power self power nembutsu non-practice translation
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:41:- Pargament religious problem solving styles self-directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:42:- spiritual materialism practice ego self-improvement Trungpa
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:43:- Cheetah House adverse meditation effects dissociation hyperarousal
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:51:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, 1988, indexed in Religious Coping, https://link.springer.com/rwe/10.1007/978-3-030-24348-7_578: overlap: Already sorts religious agency by who carries problem-solving responsibility: self, God, or collaboration.; difference: It is about coping and agency with God, not post-threshold method authority or contemplative verification.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for custody and support-locus language.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:52:- Cheetah House FAQ on meditation-related difficulties, https://www.cheetahhouse.org/faq: overlap: Supports the safety concern that practice can worsen anxiety, intrusive thoughts, dissociation, motivation, meaning, agency, and identity.; difference: It does not provide the two-axis authority model.; novelty impact: Improves safety grounding but does not increase originality.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:56:Unlike MN 22, Smith, Sells, Pargament, spiritual-materialism warnings, VCE safety work, and prior Lumenary return or custody audits, this idea says that the specific interaction between boundary operation and post-threshold custody should predict when a helpful method becomes guidance, conduct, external accountability, rest, or a private judge of worth. That is a useful synthesis, but the structure is mostly inherited from recent internal records.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:60:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, Tannisho Other Power, inherited religion with no discrete threshold, and valid daily repetition without a separable product.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:62:Why it strains the model: These cases refuse the assumed sequence of tool, result, and post-result authority. In Dogen, practice is not merely a ladder to be evaluated afterward. In Tannisho, efficacy is not owned by the practitioner or method. In inherited religion, the authority may be communal and continuous before any explicit insight. In faithful daily repetition, keeping the same form may be obedience or formation rather than self-surveillance.
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:77:- Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with Tannisho and Other Power
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:81:- Meditation safety clinicians familiar with VCE and Cheetah House cases
reviews/originality/2026-05-30-when-tools-become-judges-95d52440abfccb6a.md:90:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say this is standard raft, upaya, practice-realization, Other Power, spiritual direction, spiritual materialism warning, or ordinary supervision, with no new prediction about repair.
