reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.json:64:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization one no-threshold practice-realization"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.json:74:      "difference": "Pargament studies religious problem-solving and coping, not self-weakening contemplative paths with separate receiving-surface coding and verification practices.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-custody-and-receiving-surface-255ec907071592a1.json:77:      "source": "Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, Journal for the Scientific Study of Religion, 1988, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
