reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:89:      "source": "Pargament et al. religious problem-solving and coping styles, self-directing, deferring, collaborative, summary and scale discussion at https://pmc.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/articles/PMC1630686/ and https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:126:    "Add mandatory anomaly values: search-refusal, practice-realization, direct-recognition bypass, radical Other Power, inherited practice, cessation or nirodha, no-residue report, psychiatric vulnerability, and undecidable.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:127:    "Compare predictive power against Pargament agency styles, Katz contextualism, Lutz Phenomenological Matrix, VCE influencing factors, MPE and nondual-awareness questionnaires, Ferrer participatory theory, spiritual bypassing and spiritual materialism literature, and prior Lumenary ledgers.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:132:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.78 to about 0.52. The synthesis is useful and testable, but both halves are already present in prior Lumenary audits, and the exact upstream-downstream move is closely anticipated by Claude's Reflexivity Policy. External prior art also strongly anticipates the core structure: Pargament for agency distribution, Katz for tradition-shaped experience, Lutz for multidimensional practice coding, VCE for interpretation and management of contemplative effects, MPE and nondual-awareness research for residue-like phenomenology, and Ferrer for participatory co-creation. The remaining contribution is a separability and incremental-prediction protocol.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:135:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners say the model is ordinary agency, grace, self-power and other-power, spiritual bypassing, nondual warning, or lineage pedagogy in new language. They cannot identify predictions that differ from Pargament, VCE, Lutz, Reflexivity Policy, or existing teacher warnings.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:138:      "Is this model more than Pargament agency styles plus Katz contextualism plus Lutz or VCE practice-factor coding?",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:151:      "Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with Other Power and shinjin",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:153:      "Psychologists of religion familiar with Pargament and religious attribution"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:161:      "Dogen Bendowa and shusho itto, Soto Zen explanation with Bendowa quotation, https://global.sotozen-net.or.jp/eng/library/key_terms/pdf/key_terms07.pdf"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:164:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit used accessible primary translations, open academic articles, prior Lumenary audits, and practitioner-facing Zen sources. It did not fully review Pargament's original 1988 article, Katz's Language, Epistemology, and Mysticism, Lindbeck, Sharf, Ferrer monographs, Longchenpa in Tibetan, Sanskrit or Pali originals, or actual practitioner interviews. Novelty should not rise without those checks.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-practice-architecture-as-upstream-condition-for-remainder-phenomenology-d64d7da35f45e724.json:174:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Pargament, Katz, Lutz, VCE, MPE research, Ferrer, and prior Lumenary remainder and credit models, this idea says the key test is incremental prediction: credit distribution should partly predict when subject-shaped residue appears, while residue should still add predictive information after credit distribution and practice-reflexivity have been coded. Without that incremental result, the idea is only a refined consolidation."
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:7:Status: draft
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:15:The closest prior argument is Smith's comparison of Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein as therapeutic, ladder-like methods that remove the problems they appear to solve. The overlap is real: both see some methods as self-canceling medicine. The difference is that this finding treats self-canceling method as only one quadrant in a wider typology. It adds retained and embodied outcomes, separates validation from retention, and predicts concrete features of training systems: manuals, supervision, termination signs, relapse patterns, and ethical reentry should differ by quadrant. Sells is also close on apophatic language that unsays itself, but his focus is discourse, not the custody and post-use shape of a whole practice. The raft simile is a direct prior structure, but it also exposes the anomaly: some valid methods are neither simply confirmed nor canceled. They are validated for use, then released from identity.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:20:- Practitioner-method lens used: MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, raft simile, treated as a method for examining whether a tool remains useful after crossing, then criticized for possibly hiding communal and institutional custody.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:21:- Primary-text comparison: MN 22 says the teaching is for crossing and should not be carried after use; the Heart Sutra denies attainment while still relying on Prajnaparamita; Mandukya Upanishad identifies the fourth as the self to be known; Dogen's practice-realization identity treats practice as expression, not a discarded ladder.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:28:This model may over-systematize living traditions. Dogen strains it most because practice-realization is neither retained as a means nor abandoned after reaching a result. The practice is the expression of realization, so the two-axis model may falsely impose a before-and-after sequence. The Heart Sutra also strains it: it denies attainment while ritually preserving the text and practice that enact the denial. A practitioner may report that the method is not possessed, released, or embodied, but simply trusted within a lineage. The raft lens itself may distort the inquiry by favoring tool-use and completion over devotion, inherited belonging, grace, and lifelong communal formation.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:80:Survived critique from the raft simile, Heart Sutra no-attainment, Mandukya self-recognition, and Dogen practice-realization by narrowing the claim from method completion to post-use relation.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:152:- Result: Pending. Current near-neighbors include Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on apophatic unsaying, and MN 22's raft simile.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:162:- Result: Pending close reading of Bendowa, Genjokoan, and practitioner commentaries.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:164:- Next action: Close-read Dogen against MN 22 and the Heart Sutra with attention to result language, continuation, and conduct.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:189:- Close-read Dogen's Bendowa and Genjokoan against MN 22 and the Heart Sutra to test whether embodied practice breaks the retained versus abandoned axis or requires a third post-use category.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:190:- If this model is right, then traditions should mark different post-use instructions: Advaita-style inquiry should preserve recognition criteria, raft-like Buddhism should warn against carrying the method as identity, and practice-realization systems should shift from result language to conduct language. If these instructions do not cluster by method shape, the model is weakened.
observations/codex/2026-05-29-method-release-has-a-shape.md:193:- Protocol improvement: when using a tool-like lens such as the raft simile, pair it with a non-tool lens such as devotion, vow, or communal belonging so that completion does not become the hidden standard.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:30:Secondary literature gap: I did not find an exact three-type typology of contemplative methods as confirming, canceling, and dissolving at completion. But the self-canceling portion has very strong prior art in Nagarjuna, Wittgenstein ladder readings, Buddhist raft discussions, and Sells on apophatic unsaying. The dissolving portion is also standard in fana, zuowang, and Dzogchen descriptions. The new part is the comparative axis and its predicted consequences, not the individual patterns.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:41:- spiritual method abandon raft Upanishad Heart Sutra comparison
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:42:- Victor Hori Koan and Kensho in the Rinzai Zen Curriculum koan practice curriculum
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:49:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, raft simile, Thanissaro translation, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html: overlap: The Dhamma is a raft for crossing, to be grasped properly and then let go. This is a direct prior structure for validated-then-abandoned method.; difference: It is not simply canceling or dissolving. It validates proper use, then releases attachment after the crossing.; novelty impact: High reduction and major anomaly. It suggests a fourth pattern or a two-axis framework.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:51:- G. Victor Sogen Hori, Koan and Kensho in the Rinzai Zen Curriculum, search-accessible copy, https://docslib.org/doc/1302437/the-koan-is-said-to-pose-to-the-ze-n-practitione-r-a-parado-x-unsolvabl-e-by-the-rational-intellectualizing-mind: overlap: Directly addresses the common model of koan using reason to drive itself into self-contradiction, then complicates it by describing a curriculum after kensho.; difference: It shows that a self-canceling tool can become a highly structured authorization system, contrary to a simple prediction of transmission difficulty.; novelty impact: High reduction and anomaly for the Zen evidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:56:Unlike Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on apophatic unsaying, or the raft and ladder motifs, this idea proposes a three-way comparative axis and claims that the axis predicts verification and transmission better than doctrine alone.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:60:Candidate: Validated-then-abandoned hybrids, especially MN 22's raft, Heart Sutra reliance on Prajnaparamita after no-attainment, and Rinzai koan curriculum after kensho.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:62:Why it strains the model: These cases mix confirmation, cancellation, and dissolution across stages. The raft must be grasped properly before being released. The Heart Sutra negates attainment but retains reliance and mantra. Koan practice may exhaust conceptual striving yet becomes a formal curriculum with tests. If hybrids are normal, the three types are not stable categories.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:70:- If: Hybrid traditions should show explicit boundary management between method stages. Then: Texts should mark when to use, trust, undermine, release, or embody a method. Examples would include raft language, preliminary versus main practice, koan curriculum before and after kensho, or thorn-removing-thorn metaphors. Weakens if: No boundary markers appear, or methods freely confirm, cancel, and dissolve without any pedagogical distinction. Test surface: Historical and textual analysis of Zen, Dzogchen, Advaita, Madhyamaka, Sufi, and Christian apophatic training sequences.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:87:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say every serious path already uses all three stages, or identify the model as a familiar upaya, raft, ladder, no-thesis, fana, or Gelassenheit pattern with new labels.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:112:- Close-read Mandukya, Heart Sutra, MN 22, Vigrahavyavartani 29, and Hori's koan curriculum before treating the three types as stable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-method-s-reckoning-what-a-practice-does-with-its-own-authority-at-completion-54774578d7528e56.md:113:- Search further for upaya, raft, ladder, thorn-removes-thorn, Gelassenheit, fana and baqa, rang grol, and practice-realization as exact structural near-neighbors.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "No-threshold entry: inherited practice and Dogen's practice-realization grammar, especially Bendowa's claim that beginner practice is already original realization and that there is no beginning in practice.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:28:      "expected_observation": "In paired communities with similar diaspora context, demographics, institutional density, and teacher access, Other Power or grace grammars will produce more warnings against self-powered calculation, more trust and receiving language, and different repair instructions than effort-centered traditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:56:    "Pargament religion problem solving process three styles coping self directing deferring collaborative",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:59:    "Tannisho Shinran Other Power self power nembutsu not practice good act chapter 8 translation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:62:    "Dogen Bendowa practice realization beginner practice realization translation",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:75:      "novelty_impact": "High reduction for agency-locus claims. Moderate remaining novelty if the ledger predicts entry safeguards beyond Pargament's styles.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:76:      "overlap": "Close for responsibility distribution. Pargament already distinguishes self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious problem-solving styles by how agency is assigned between person and God.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:77:      "source": "Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:98:      "difference": "Shinran gives one path grammar, not a cross-tradition predictive rubric.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:99:      "novelty_impact": "High reduction and high anomaly pressure. The model must avoid recoding Other Power as an analyst-owned capacity.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:100:      "overlap": "Very close for forbidden self-claiming and load relocation. Shinran explicitly treats Other Power as decisive and denies that nembutsu is self-power practice.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:101:      "source": "Shinran, Chapter on Practice, Collected Works of Shinran, https://shinranworks.com/the-major-expositions/chapter-on-practice/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:136:    "Do not raise above novel_synthesis unless split-source blind coding predicts safeguards or failure modes better than conversion studies, Pargament agency styles, upaya, liminality, situated-learning, and religious-socialization variables."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:138:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.82 to about 0.64. The distributed-entry and threshold pieces are strongly anticipated by Rambo's conversion model, liminality, situated learning, religious socialization, upaya, Pargament's agency styles, Engler's prerequisites, Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic grammar, and Shinran's Other Power. The remaining contribution is a promising operational synthesis: a split-source predictive rubric linking entry capacity loci to tradition-specific warning and repair patterns.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:151:      "Jodo Shinshu ministers and Shinran scholars",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:164:      "Shinran, Chapter on Practice, Collected Works of Shinran, plus Tannisho, Matheson Trust page, https://shinranworks.com/the-major-expositions/chapter-on-practice/ and https://www.themathesontrust.org/library/tannisho-shin-buddhist-aphorisms"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:167:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The audit searched conversion theory, religious coping, legitimate peripheral participation, liminality, upaya, transformative learning, religious socialization, Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic model, Shinran, SN 45.8, Dogen, Augustine, and the Council of Orange. It did not sufficiently close-read Kyogyoshinsho beyond the Chapter on Practice, Augustine and Pelagius in full primary-text sequence, Longchenpa or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, Sufi bayah and fana texts, or original-language terms for entrusting, effort, vow, grace, and capacity. That gap blocks a candidate-discovery claim.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:168:    "structural_observation": "SN 45.8 makes the path legible through cultivated factors: right view, right resolve, right effort, right mindfulness, and right concentration are named as functions a practitioner develops. Shinran's Chapter on Practice reverses the ownership grammar: nembutsu is not self-power practice, Other Power is the decisive cause, and the Name or Primal Vow carries the decisive function. This supports the ledger's contrast because similar threshold functions are allocated to different loci. It also threatens the model because Pure Land sources may reject the analyst's capacity language rather than merely move capacity from practitioner to vow."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-entry-state-ledger-4299246a4ab81e4e.json:177:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike conversion-process theory, religious coping theory, upaya pedagogy, situated learning, liminality theory, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar model, Engler's capacity prerequisites, and Shinran's Other Power grammar, this idea claims that path entry can be coded as a pre-practice distributed ledger plus a normative beginning grammar, and that this pairing should predict later safeguards, warnings, verification practices, and failure modes better than either entry ecology or doctrine alone."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:10:    "Comparison must first preserve the transformation register, such as human effort, Other Power, primordial awareness, practice-realization, divine restoration, or causal continuity.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:20:    "prediction": "Different change registers should produce different warning profiles: CBT should warn about distorted appraisal and homework nonuse, psychoanalysis about resistance and enactment, somatic therapy about dysregulation and bypassing body signals, twelve-step work about self-will and isolation, ACT about experiential avoidance and fusion.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:28:      "expected_observation": "Tannisho, Shinran letters, and Jodo Shinshu teaching materials should warn more against self-power, calculation, pride in practice, and self-assessment than against laxity as the primary danger.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:29:      "if_model_is_right": "Other Power texts should show a distinctive warning profile after the register is identified.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:31:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Other Power materials do not warn against calculation more than effort-centered manuals, or the warnings track genre, polemic, or institution better than transformation register."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:35:      "if_model_is_right": "Direct-introduction traditions should show a warning profile distinct from Other Power traditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:42:      "test_surface": "Bendowa, Genjokoan, selected Shobogenzo fascicles, Soto practice manuals, and teacher interviews.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:46:      "expected_observation": "Independent coders should infer later manual warnings from early register statements at above-chance rates, for example calculation in Shinran, misrecognition in Dzogchen, wrong effort in gradual paths, and conceptual reification in apophatic or raft-like traditions.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:49:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Predictions are vague, post hoc, low agreement, or no better than Pargament-style agency categories, direct textual summary, or broad tradition labels."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:55:    "Tannisho chapter 11 self power calculation Other Power text",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:56:    "Tannisho chapter 8 nembutsu not practice good act Shinran pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:57:    "Dogen Bendowa practice-realization training and enlightenment are one text",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:63:    "Pargament religion problem-solving process three styles of coping",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:98:      "difference": "Pargament is psychological and coping-focused. The candidate uses primary-text registers of salvation, awakening, or realization and asks what vulnerabilities each tradition itself names.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:100:      "overlap": "Close for agency distribution. Pargament already distinguishes self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious problem-solving styles involving different relationships between person and God.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:101:      "source": "Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:104:      "difference": "MN 22 is a Buddhist internal teaching about the right use of doctrine, not a comparative rubric field.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:107:      "source": "MN 22, The Water-Snake Simile, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:110:      "difference": "Dzogchen sources provide one register and its risks. The candidate compares that register with Other Power, practice-realization, divine restoration, and effortful paths without reducing them to one agency model.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:120:    "Test primary texts before broad tradition labels: Tannisho chapters 1, 6, 8, 10, and 11; Shinran letters; Bendowa or Genjokoan; one Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manual; one Christian grace or apophatic source; and one Sufi fana or baqa source.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:123:    "Read Freiberger, Clooney, Hedges, Katz, Sharf, Lindbeck, Pargament, Shinran scholarship, Dogen practice-realization scholarship, upaya literature, and apophatic theology before raising novelty above extended."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:125:  "novelty_adjustment": "Reduce novelty from 0.68 to about 0.56. The register-first discipline is strongly anticipated by comparative theology, hermeneutics, contextualist mysticism scholarship, Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic model, Sharf's critique of generic experience, Pargament's agency styles, Shinran's Other Power, Dogen's practice-realization, and MN 22's self-limiting doctrine use. The remaining contribution is a useful operational extension with predictive fields, not a discovery.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:128:    "answers_that_reduce_originality": "Practitioners and scholars say this is standard comparative theology, upaya, self-power versus Other Power, practice-realization, apophatic self-limitation, cultural-linguistic theology, or religious coping theory. They also say the rubric does not change teaching decisions or predict student failure modes.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:137:      "Jodo Shinshu ministers and Shinran scholars",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:147:      "Shinran, Tannisho, especially chapters 1, 6, 8, 10, and 11, trans. Taitetsu Unno, https://www.themathesontrust.org/papers/fareasternreligions/Tannisho-Unno.pdf",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:148:      "Dogen, Bendowa, especially sections 3, 4, 7, and 10, https://www.abuddhistlibrary.com/Buddhism/C%20-%20Zen/Ancestors/Dogen/Bendowa/Bendowa.htm"
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:151:    "secondary_literature_gap": "The closest scholarly prior art includes Oliver Freiberger on comparison as selection, description, juxtaposition, redescription, rectification, and theory formation; Paul Hedges on comparative theology and hermeneutics; Francis Clooney's comparative theology; Katz and Sharf on contextualist and anti-experience-flattening method; Lindbeck's cultural-linguistic model; and Pargament's religious problem-solving styles. The audit did not fully close-read Clooney, Lindbeck, Dzogchen root texts, Meister Eckhart, Qushayri, Ibn Arabi, or Shinran's letters. That gap prevents any candidate-discovery claim.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:152:    "structural_observation": "The Tannisho strongly supports the register-first move. Its decisive register is Other Power, and it names boundary failures such as self-power, calculation, doubt, wrong teacher ownership, and confusing nembutsu with the practitioner's own good act. Bendowa is the anomaly case. It names wrong understanding, false teachers, verbal clinging, and inadequate practice, but its register is practice-realization, where training and enlightenment are not two. The proposed model reads Shinran well, but its interface language strains Dogen because an interface can imply the very separation between practitioner, practice, and realization that Bendowa rejects."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-register-sensitive-path-interface-35681329dc02292c.json:161:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike Freiberger, Clooney, Hedges, Katz, Sharf, Lindbeck, Pargament, Shinran, Dogen, and MN 22, this idea claims that comparative work should use a specific two-layer rubric: preserve the transformation register first, then code only tradition-named vulnerabilities, safeguards, and warnings against the rubric itself. Its contribution is operational and predictive, not the discovery that traditions have different registers."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:25:- Tannisho sections 1, 6, and 8, Taitetsu Unno translation, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:28:Structural observation: Tannisho layers beginning through entrusting, Amida's Primal Vow, teacher humility, and a refusal to claim disciples or self-owned merit. SN 45.8 layers the path through trainable functions: view, resolve, speech, action, livelihood, effort, mindfulness, and concentration. The contrast supports the candidate's agency-authorization intuition, but it also shows that the strongest pieces are already visible in primary texts and prior Lumenary entry-claimant work.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:30:Secondary literature gap: Search covered conversion-stage theory, religious coping agency styles, plausibility structures, liminality, situated learning, doctrine-as-grammar, scaffolding, Shinran Other Power, Tannisho, SN 45.8, and Soto practice-realization. It did not fully close-read Rambo's full monograph, Lindbeck's full book, Dzogchen pointing-out manuals, Calvinist and Wesleyan entry sermons, Gelug lamrim texts, Sufi bayah sources, or psychotherapy alliance literature. That gap blocks candidate-discovery status.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:37:- Pargament religious problem solving styles self-directing deferring collaborative
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:42:- Shinran Other Power self power Primal Vow Name
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:48:- Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, summary at https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for distributing agency among human and divine actors through self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles.; difference: The candidate applies agency distribution to entry warnings, repair, and cross-tradition authorization.; novelty impact: Large reduction for agency-distribution logic. The remaining contribution is threshold-specific operationalization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:54:- Shinran, Chapter on Practice, Collected Works of Shinran, https://shinranworks.com/the-major-expositions/chapter-on-practice/: overlap: Very close for relocating decisive practice and beginning to Other Power, the Name, and the Primal Vow rather than self-owned effort.; difference: The candidate generalizes this as one case in a cross-tradition coding model.; novelty impact: High reduction and anomaly pressure. The model must not smuggle self-power language into a tradition that rejects it.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:60:Unlike Rambo's conversion stages, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament's religious agency styles, Lave and Wenger's situated learning, liminality theory, scaffolding theory, Shinran's Other Power grammar, and prior Lumenary entry-claimant work, this idea says beginning should be coded as four separable layers: empirical affordance, institutional selection, normative agency authorization, and repeated handoff density. Its possible contribution is not that beginnings are layered, but that these layers can be split into independent corpora and tested for prediction of warnings, repair instructions, and reauthorization episodes.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:72:- If: Entry grammar can be coded from doctrinal or initiation texts independently of pastoral manuals. Then: Blind coders using only entry texts should predict later warning profiles, such as pride warnings in self-effort paths, passivity warnings in grace or Other Power paths, and teacher-dependence warnings in recognition-based paths, above baseline models. Weakens if: Warnings are predicted equally well or better by institutional role, teacher style, social context, or conversion-stage variables, with no added value from agency authorization grammar. Test surface: Split-corpus coding across Zen, Jodo Shinshu, Calvinist, Wesleyan, Dzogchen, Gelug, and Sufi entry materials.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:80:- Jodo Shinshu ministers and Shinran scholars
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:116:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.70 to about 0.55. The layered beginning structure is strongly anticipated by Rambo conversion theory, liminality, situated learning, scaffolding, Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Berger plausibility structures, Shinran Other Power, Dogen practice-realization, and prior Lumenary entry-claimant records. The remaining contribution is an extension: a split-corpus coding protocol that asks whether affordance, institutional selection, authorization grammar, and handoff density predict warnings and repair episodes without circular evidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-layered-authorization-of-beginning-8a8d544ce3b6f17a.md:123:- Run baseline comparisons against Rambo conversion stages, Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck grammar, liminality, legitimate peripheral participation, scaffolding, upaya, religious socialization, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:18:- Different primary texts model different endings: MN 22 releases the raft after right use, Heart Sutra negates attainment while retaining reliance, Mandukya allows a known Self, Rinzai koan work exhausts ordinary thinking while remaining curriculum, and Dogen collapses before and after through practice-realization.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:26:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, raft simile, Thanissaro Bhikkhu translation, https://www.accesstoinsight.org/tipitaka/mn/mn.022.than.html
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:29:Structural observation: MN 22 is a close primary near-neighbor for validated-then-released method. It teaches right grasp, crossing, and release of the raft, so the candidate's set-down category is old. The Heart Sutra complicates the model because it negates attainment yet retains reliance on Prajnaparamita and mantra. This supports the candidate's claim that undermining result does not always mean abandoning method. Mandukya adds a different pressure: negation culminates in the Self that is to be known. Dogen strains the whole after-completion frame because practice and realization are inseparable, so return is not a later test but the practice itself.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:31:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors in Smith on Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Sells on unsaying, Asad, Lindbeck, Sharf, VCE, Hadot-style spiritual exercises, Zen oxherding return motifs, and Buddhist raft or upaya literature. It did not read the full books by Smith, Sells, Hadot, Hori, Lindbeck, Katz, or Sharf, and it did not consult original Sanskrit, Pali, Chinese, Japanese, Greek, Latin, Arabic, or Tibetan.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:37:- "raft simile" "not for holding onto" MN 22 method release
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:41:- "Dogen" "practice and realization are one" Bendowa
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:46:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, https://www.accesstoinsight.org/tipitaka/mn/mn.022.than.html: overlap: Direct primary near-neighbor. It already gives a method-use test: use the raft to cross, then do not carry it as possession.; difference: The candidate broadens the raft logic into a three-way return rubric and applies it to achievement-contingent self-worth.; novelty impact: Strong downgrade. The release side is known.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:47:- Shorter Heart Sutra, https://en.wikisource.org/wiki/Translation:Shorter_Praj%C3%B1%C4%81p%C4%81ramit%C4%81_H%E1%B9%9Bdaya_S%C5%ABtra: overlap: Very close for the category of undermined attainment with retained reliance. It denies attainment yet keeps Prajnaparamita and mantra operative.; difference: The candidate treats this as one cell in a comparative rubric rather than as Mahayana teaching in its own right.; novelty impact: Downgrades novelty but supports the model's refusal to make raft-release universal.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:48:- Dogen Bendowa material, Everyday Zen Foundation, https://everydayzen.org/teachings/dogens-bendowa-part-2-of-3/: overlap: Close anomaly and near-neighbor. Dogen's practice-realization already says practice is not a means to a later result and realization is not an object privately recognized after practice.; difference: The candidate makes Dogen an anomaly inside a return model, whereas Dogen may reject the whole before, peak, after sequence.; novelty impact: Lowers confidence. If Dogen is central rather than marginal, the return test may be only an external heuristic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:56:Unlike the raft simile, apophatic unsaying, therapeutic readings of Nagarjuna and Wittgenstein, Dogen practice-realization, VCE aftercare, Asad's discursive tradition, and Lindbeck's doctrine grammar, this idea's distinct claim is a practical comparative test: code whether a method validates or undermines the result, then code whether the method is retained, released, or embodied, and see whether that interaction predicts warnings, re-entry duties, identity risks, and repairs better than doctrine, institution, teacher style, or clinical-risk variables alone.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:60:Candidate: Dogen practice-realization, radical Other Power in Tannisho, inherited communal religion, and successful ordinary ethical practice without a marked peak experience.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:62:Why it strains the model: These cases resist the sequence of method, result, and return. Dogen makes practice and realization inseparable. Tannisho relocates efficacy to Amida's Vow and can make nembutsu non-practice from the practitioner's side. Inherited religion may not have a discrete completion event. Ordinary ethical formation may return without peak experience at all.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:64:Confidence effect: Prevents candidate-discovery status. The model is useful as a heuristic only if it can code no-threshold, no-peak, Other Power, inherited practice, and practice-realization without forcing them into a modern after-experience frame.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:70:- If: Cross-training will expose different return grammars. Then: Practitioners trained in Advaita inquiry, Prajnaparamita practice, raft-style early Buddhist training, and Soto practice-realization will describe different appropriate relations to insight: stable recognition, resisted attainment, released tool, or ongoing practice-conduct identity. Weakens if: Practitioners converge on the same return rule after controlling for teacher and personality, or differences reduce to vocabulary without behavioral, warning, or repair consequences. Test surface: Dual-trained practitioner interviews and behavior-coded follow-up after comparable retreat experiences.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:75:- Theravada monastics and lay teachers familiar with MN 22 and raft simile
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:79:- Jodo Shinshu teachers familiar with Tannisho and Other Power
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:88:Answers that reduce originality: Teachers recognize the rubric as ordinary raft teaching, upaya, practice-realization, apophatic unsaying, koan curriculum, spiritual exercise, aftercare, or ethics of fruits, and say it does not predict guidance beyond existing lineage rules.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:108:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.58 to 0.41. The teaching line is strong and publishable only as a restrained synthesis for achievement-contingent self-worth. The research model should be treated as extended prior art until it predicts warnings, repairs, or return duties better than existing upaya, raft, apophatic, practice-realization, spiritual-exercises, VCE, authority, and grammar frameworks.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:114:- Add mandatory anomaly values for practice-realization, radical Other Power, inherited religion, no-threshold practice, no-peak ethical formation, direct recognition, and clinician-held support.
reviews/originality/2026-05-28-the-test-is-how-you-return-b463ae0abb9b554d.md:116:- Close-read Tannisho, Dogen Bendowa or Genjokoan, a Rinzai koan curriculum source, Cloud of Unknowing or Dionysius, a Dzogchen pointing-out source, and one Sufi fana or baqa source before raising source reliability.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-compound-entry-grammar-f417ef646f5066fa.json:30:      "test_surface": "Split-source coding across Orange and Augustinian grace texts, Tannisho and Shinran letters, Dzogchen or Mahamudra pointing-out manuals, and matched Theravada or Confucian cultivation texts.",
