reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:47:- Dogen Bendowa practice and realization are one primary text
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:53:- Tannisho, Unno translation, https://www.themathesontrust.org/papers/fareasternreligions/Tannisho-Unno.pdf; Shinran Notes, https://shinranworks.com/commentaries/notes-on-once-calling-and-many-calling/: overlap: Very close for sharp boundary, Other Power source, refusal of calculation, and warnings about claiming the practice as one's own.; difference: The candidate turns Shinran's internal grammar into a cross-tradition coding instrument.; novelty impact: Large reduction for the formal-marker and reappropriation layers in Pure Land cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:56:- Dogen, Bendowa practice-realization, https://buddhismnow.com/2023/10/08/practice-within-realisation-dogen/: overlap: Close as an anomaly: practice and realization are inseparable, with no clean boundary in realization and no beginning in practice.; difference: The candidate can handle Dogen only if it allows no-boundary and analyst-frame-refused values.; novelty impact: Reduces universality. It forces the rubric to become a local heuristic rather than a master structure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:57:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for agency allocation among self-directing, deferring, and collaborative religious styles.; difference: Pargament is not stage-sensitive contemplative-path analysis and does not model dissolution gradients.; novelty impact: Moderate reduction for the credit-distribution axis.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:58:- Steve Bein, Self Power, Other Power, and Non-dualism in Japanese Buddhism, https://philpapers.org/rec/BEISPO: overlap: Close for comparing self-power, other-power, and nondualism as agency structures in Japanese Buddhism.; difference: The candidate adds warning clusters, stage intervals, and gradient afterwork.; novelty impact: Moderate to large reduction, especially for Japanese Buddhist agency comparison.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:66:Unlike Khemaka, Shinran, Dzogchen instructions, Dogen, Pargament, Bein, Trungpa, VCE, and prior Lumenary ledgers, this idea says the comparative unit is a two-track transfer profile and predicts that safeguards cluster where formal agency grammar changes while partial dissolution leaves layer-specific reappropriation risks.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:87:- Jodo Shinshu ministers familiar with shinjin and Other Power
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:99:- Does this rubric identify a repair that would not already come from spiritual materialism, upaya, religious coping, or ordinary teacher experience?
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:102:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners say this is standard fetter theory, Shinshu non-calculation, Dzogchen stabilization, spiritual materialism, upaya, or ordinary pastoral caution. They cannot name repairs beyond familiar warnings about pride, striving, doubt, role identity, or teacher dependence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:122:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.61 to about 0.54. The two-track formulation is useful, but the primary-text close read shows that formal attainment versus residual self-claiming is already explicit in SN 22.89, Other Power boundary and anti-calculation repair are explicit in Shinran, and reappropriation is strongly anticipated by spiritual materialism. The remaining contribution is a comparative coding synthesis with testable warning-cluster predictions.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:129:- Add mandatory values for no-boundary, no-threshold, inherited-practice, practice-realization, Other Power refusal, recognition-event, continuous authorization, and undecidable.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.md:131:- Compare predictive value against Pargament agency styles, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Trungpa spiritual materialism, VCE contextual factors, upaya pedagogy, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:27:- Shinran and Rennyo, Tannisho and Ofumi, BDK English Tripitaka, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:31:Structural observation: Orange is the strongest prescriptive incapacity case: faith's beginning, desire, assent, prayer, and right choice are assigned to grace rather than unaided natural power. Tannisho and Ofumi give a vow-held analogue: entrusting is given by Amida's working, nenbutsu after settled faith is gratitude rather than self-powered production, and the warning profile targets calculation and self-power. Benedict gives institutional and apprenticeship custody: the novice is delayed, tested, placed under a senior, repeatedly exposed to the Rule, and only then incorporated. SN 55.5 is a partial anomaly: it names association with people of integrity, hearing true Dhamma, appropriate attention, and practice in accordance with Dhamma. That is distributed support, but not necessarily a doctrine forbidding self-generated beginning. The close-read result is that the candidate's structure exists in several sources, but its categories are analyst abstractions over older grace, vow, rule, apprenticeship, and stream-entry grammars.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:44:- Pargament religion problem-solving self-directing deferring collaborative agency
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:46:- Tannisho Other Power self-power entrusting Primal Vow
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:58:- Kenneth Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for distributing agency between person and God through self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles, with different practical outcomes.; difference: Pargament studies coping and problem solving, not initiation or the first authorization of transformative practice under grace, vow, teacher, rule, ritual, or community custody.; novelty impact: High reduction for agency-distribution and self-agency claims.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:60:- Shinran and Rennyo, Tannisho and Ofumi, https://bdk.or.jp/document/dgtl-dl/dBET_Tannisho-Ofumi_1996.pdf: overlap: Near exact for vow-held beginning, Other Power, blocked self-credit, critique of calculation, and gratitude rather than self-powered production after entrusting.; difference: Pure Land texts are primary cases, not a general theory of prescriptive versus retrospective custody.; novelty impact: Very high reduction for vow-held and anti-self-power examples.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:66:Unlike prior Lumenary entry ledgers, Rambo conversion theory, legitimate peripheral participation, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Pargament's agency styles, Orange, Shinran, Benedict, and OCIA, this candidate's only distinct claim is that beginnings should be coded as custody of unstable attention, trust, agency, and interpretation, and that entry doctrine should be classified as either retrospective narration or prescriptive control. That difference is useful but thin, because prior Lumenary records and older sources already contain most of the structure.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:78:- If: Prescriptive custody grammar has incremental predictive force after social, institutional, and conversion-process controls. Then: Coders using only entry or doctrinal texts should predict held-out beginner warnings, verification rules, and repair instructions better when custody holder and prescriptive versus retrospective function are added to Rambo-style and Lave-Wenger-style variables. Weakens if: The added fields do not improve prediction, or all signal is absorbed by institution, teacher authority, socialization, ritual process, clinical risk, or tradition identity. Test surface: Split-source blind coding across Orange, Tannisho or Ofumi, Benedictine novitiate texts, OCIA, SN 55.5 and related Theravada manuals, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra entry source, and one Sufi or Islamic initiation source.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:104:Answers that reduce originality: Practitioners and scholars say the frame is ordinary grace theology, Other Power, catechumenate, monastic formation, refuge, initiation, lineage pedagogy, doctrine-as-grammar, religious coping, conversion studies, or legitimate peripheral participation. They cannot identify repairs predicted by custody grammar beyond institution, teacher experience, community ecology, temperament, or clinical risk.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:124:Novelty adjustment: Reduce novelty from 0.76 to about 0.43. The candidate is generative, but most of its structure is already present in local Lumenary records, especially Entry-State Ledger, Threshold Grammar Under Translation Strain, Compound Entry Grammar, Layered Authorization of Beginning, and Operational Remainder Ecology. External near-neighbors further reduce the claim: Rambo covers conversion process, Lave and Wenger cover pre-mastery participation, Kupari and Utriainen apply that to religious newcomers, Lindbeck covers doctrine as grammar, Pargament covers agency distribution, Orange and Shinran give near-exact prescriptive beginning cases, Benedict and OCIA give institutional formation cases. The remaining contribution is a sharper label for prescriptive versus retrospective custody, not a discovery-level idea.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-prescriptive-custody-of-beginnings-7a1a4b07a241a1b9.md:134:- Compare predictive value against Rambo conversion stages, Lofland-Stark conversion conditions, Van Gennep and Turner liminality, Lindbeck doctrine-as-grammar, Lave and Wenger legitimate peripheral participation, Kupari and Utriainen ritual-learning data, Pargament agency styles, catechumenate scholarship, monastic formation scholarship, upaya pedagogy, VCE factor coding, and prior Lumenary ledgers.
observations/codex/2026-05-26-the-licensed-training-mistake.md:7:Status: draft
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:27:- MN 22 Alagaddupama Sutta, Heart Sutra, Shinran On Jinen-Honi, and Dogen Bendowa or practice-realization sources, https://www.dhammatalks.org/suttas/MN/MN22.html, https://www.lotsawahouse.org/words-of-the-buddha/heart-sutra, https://shinranworks.com/letters/lamp-for-the-latter-ages/on-jinen-honi-1258/, https://buddhismnow.com/2023/10/08/practice-within-realisation-dogen/
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:29:Structural observation: Ignatius is the closest primary-text neighbor. The director adapts exercises to the exercitant, receives reports of movements and thoughts, reveals dangerous secrecy to a confessor or spiritual person, and is also restrained from seizing the exercitant's final choice. The scruple notes already distinguish useful sensitivity from harmful over-fineness and counsel a mean. MN 22 adds that the raft must be grasped correctly before release, so release is not a generic self-check. The Heart Sutra denies attainment while retaining reliance on Prajnaparamita. Shinran and Dogen strain the whole model because no-calculation and practice-realization refuse a clean separable product that the practitioner can audit.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:31:Secondary literature gap: Still needs full reading of Ignatian directorial manuals, contemporary spiritual direction ethics, AA sponsorship sources, ERP and scrupulosity treatment literature, VCE person-centered support, spiritual bypassing literature, and achievement-contingent self-worth studies before practice publication.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:39:- Pargament religion problem solving self directing deferring collaborative coping
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:43:- spiritual bypassing Welwood Trungpa practice ego avoidance accountability
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:47:- Internal Lumenary record: Who Holds The Gate, supplied in recent originality audits.: overlap: Extremely close. It already states the three-gate structure: result-language permission, current bypassing versus self-scoring risk, and diagnostic custody.; difference: This candidate changes the public line and practice wording, but does not add a new structural variable beyond the gate-holder model.; novelty impact: Major downgrade. Treat as a renamed sibling unless separability testing proves a different prediction.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:49:- Pargament et al., Religion and the Problem-Solving Process: Three Styles of Coping, 1988, https://icmglt.org/icmlibrary/religion-and-the-problem-solving-process-three-styles-of-coping/: overlap: Close for support locus and agency distribution: self-directing, deferring, and collaborative styles already sort who is experienced as carrying problem-solving responsibility.; difference: It concerns coping with God and agency, not post-practice diagnostics, result-language checks, or self-worth scoring.; novelty impact: Reduces novelty for custody language, leaves room only for a narrower practice-safety extension.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:56:Unlike Ignatian direction, Pargament agency styles, VCE support mapping, ERP anti-reassurance rules, and the prior Lumenary Who Holds The Gate record, this candidate says that a post-practice check must first ask who should hold the diagnostic today, because the same check can repair bypassing and worsen achievement-contingent self-scoring. That distinction is useful, but it is mostly a renamed and narrower safety-routing heuristic.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:69:- If: Practitioners using insight to avoid responsibility need a self-held return-to-conduct check more than they need rest from checking. Then: In high-bypass, low-self-scoring participants, a single conduct check increases repair behavior and reduces avoidance without increasing shame. Weakens if: The conduct check does not improve behavior, or it increases self-scoring at the same rate as in the compulsive scorer group. Test surface: Screened practice pilot with spiritual bypassing, avoidance, self-worth contingency, and next-day conduct measures.
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-not-every-check-should-be-yours-b9a584e898d8b829.md:111:Novelty adjustment: Lower novelty from 0.57 to 0.28. The core is already present in the supplied Who Holds The Gate audit and has close external neighbors in Ignatian direction, spiritual direction, Pargament agency styles, contemplative adverse-effects support, ERP anti-reassurance rules, and self-focused-attention research. Human-condition fit is real but bounded: it serves stable high-achievement practitioners, founders, students, creators, caregivers, and self-directed meditators who convert insight into worth evidence. It is not for acute crisis, mania, psychosis, severe depression, dissociation, addiction withdrawal, active OCD or scrupulosity reassurance loops, abusive authority settings, or people whose main need is restored self-trust.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen's Bendowa practice-realization, especially the claim that training and enlightenment are not two, https://www.abuddhistlibrary.com/Buddhism/C%20-%20Zen/Ancestors/Dogen/Bendowa/Bendowa.htm",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:29:      "expected_observation": "Independent coders should infer later manual warnings and safeguards from early claims about self, liberation, and final transformation at above-chance rates. For example, Other Power texts should warn against calculation, practice-realization texts should warn against treating practice as a means to a later goal, and deconstructive paths should warn against reification and dissociation.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:31:      "test_surface": "Blind coding trial across SN 45.8, Tannisho, Bendowa, one Dzogchen or Mahamudra manual, one Christian grace manual, and one Sufi fana or baqa source.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:32:      "would_weaken_or_falsify": "Scalar maturity, broad tradition labels, or Pargament-style agency locus predict the same warnings as well as the vector ledger, or coders cannot agree on direction and locus."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-vector-capacity-ledger-08ac38c26b5e49aa.json:49:      "test_surface": "Practitioner-scholar interviews and manual coding of Shinran, pointing-out instructions, and grace texts.",
