reviews/originality/2026-05-26-the-transfer-profile-formal-boundaries-and-dissolution-gradients-in-contemplative-practice-92ca8dca94e1acc0.json:155:      "Does this rubric identify a repair that would not already come from spiritual materialism, upaya, religious coping, or ordinary teacher experience?",
