reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.json:133:    "secondary_literature_gap": "This audit did not read full Cassian, Evagrius, Teresa of Avila, John of the Cross, Jonathan Edwards, contemporary spiritual-direction manuals, full Hori, full Katz, full Sharf, or Cheetah House materials. No teachers, clinicians, or solo practitioners were interviewed.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.json:134:    "structural_observation": "MN 22 is already a strong source for this structure. Arittha's private interpretation is challenged by monks and then by the Buddha before the raft simile appears, and the text pairs right grasp with later release. Ignatius gives an even closer practitioner rule: after a consolation, later resolutions and opinions need examination before being trusted. Together they already contain the core pattern, experience or method may be valid, but interpretation still needs correction."
reviews/originality/2026-05-29-keep-what-can-correct-you-8144312cebdf1b38.json:146:  "unlike_statement": "Unlike MN 22, Ignatian discernment, VCE, James, Asad, Lindbeck, Sells, and the prior Lumenary recognition-gap audit, this idea's possible contribution is a narrow safety heuristic: after method release, verify that some trustworthy correction path remains, and test whether naming that path reduces inflation, shame, and isolated overinterpretation without increasing dependency."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:25:- Dogen, Genjokoan, Shohaku Okumura translation, https://brightwayzen.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/For-BWZ-Chant-Book-Genjokoan.pdf
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:27:- The Tannisho, Taitetsu Unno translation, https://nembutsu.cc/buddhism/the-tannisho/tannisho-sections-i-to-x/
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:30:Structural observation: The primary texts support boundary-first reading, but they also reduce novelty. Dogen strains a completion-boundary model because practice and realization are not cleanly sequential, realization is expressed through ongoing practice and verification by all things. Teresa repeatedly subordinates extraordinary experience to discernment, obedience, humility, Christological memory, and conduct, so authority is distributed through confessor, church, fruits, and suspicion of private certainty. The Tannisho relocates decisive efficacy away from self-owned practice and teacherly possession into Other Power, while still policing divergence through lineage memory and warnings against self-calculation. MN 10 gives a practice grammar of ardency, mindfulness, clear comprehension, hindrance work, arising and passing, and relinquishment, but it does not by itself establish later institutional teaching authorization. The close read supports the ecology claim, yet the need to separate realization, recognition, authorization, and conduct is already visible in the sources.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:32:Secondary literature gap: The audit found strong near-neighbors in Asad's discursive tradition, Weber's sociology of religious authority, Lindbeck's doctrine-as-grammar, Sharf's critique of experience as an authorization category, Katz's contextualism, Catherine Bell's ritualization and power theory, Foucault's technologies of the self, Hadot's spiritual exercises, Lave and Wenger's communities of practice, Hori's Rinzai koan curriculum, and VCE-style contemplative science factor coding. It did not fully read all monographs, original Japanese, Spanish, Pali, Arabic, or Tibetan terms, and it did not interview teachers or institutional historians. This limits confidence.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:34:Risk of overread: High. A boundary can be retrospectively constructed wherever a tradition has teachers, texts, warnings, or institutions. The model risks becoming unfalsifiable unless the boundary is coded from a held-out source before predicting transmission, warning, and repair patterns. Some traditions reject the analyst's boundary frame, especially Dogen-style practice-realization, radical Other Power, inherited religion, charismatic antinomian movements, lay devotional continuity, and traditions where realization is private but teaching authorization is institutional or political.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:41:- Rinzai Zen koan curriculum teacher testing authorization Hori
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:43:- Dogen practice realization transmission authority Genjokoan Bendowa
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:57:- G. Victor Sogen Hori, Teaching and Learning in the Rinzai Zen Monastery, Cambridge record, https://www.cambridge.org/core/books/abs/teaching-and-learning-in-japan/teaching-and-learning-in-the-rinzai-zen-monastery/06E010651A6042E1FF3EC9BE242460D9: overlap: Close within one tradition. Hori shows that koan practice, kensho language, teacher testing, curriculum, ritual formalism, and mystical insight are institutionally mediated rather than reducible to private experience.; difference: Single-tradition depth source, not a cross-tradition predictive theory.; novelty impact: High reduction for Zen cases and for the warning that completion must be read through native authorization protocols.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:62:Unlike Asad, Lindbeck, Weber, Sharf, Katz, Bell, Foucault, Hadot, Hori, VCE, and prior Lumenary ledgers, the surviving distinct claim is a split-source predictive procedure: first code native authority-boundaries from one corpus, then code reflexive operations, then test whether those operations predict transmission, teaching permission, warnings, ethical re-entry, and repair patterns better than tradition identity, metaphysical content, social ecology, institution type, and teacher style. The broader claim that maturity is governed by authority, grammar, practice, institution, and conduct is not original.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:66:Candidate: Dogen's practice-realization identity, inherited religious continuity, and radical Other Power cases.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:68:Why it strains the model: If practice and realization are not two moments, or if authorization is continuous rather than a boundary event, the phrase 'at the edge of contemplative practice' misleads. Dogen can make the whole practice field the realization, not a completion threshold. Inherited religion and lay devotion can mature through continuity, community, and repetition without a distinct arrival point. Tannisho-style Other Power can reject the idea that the practitioner or teacher owns the decisive boundary.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:70:Confidence effect: Reduces confidence in a boundary-centered version. The model should add no-boundary, continuous authorization, practice-realization, inherited continuity, radical Other Power, no-authorization-frame, and analyst-frame-refused values before treating boundary ecology as universal.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-authority-boundary-ecology-0739a5567c106853.md:131:- Use Dogen practice-realization, radical Other Power, inherited religion, charismatic antinomian movements, and realization-without-teaching-authorization cases as anomaly tests.
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.json:4:    "anomaly_candidate": "Dogen-style practice-realization, inherited devotional practice, radical Other Power, and secular mindfulness adverse effects strain the model from different sides.",
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.json:6:    "why_it_breaks_or_strains_model": "Practice-realization can refuse a before-and-after account in which capacity remains and then receives a residue label. Inherited practice may work through ritual and community before explicit doctrine is understood. Other Power can treat naming receptivity as a capacity as a self-power distortion. Secular mindfulness adverse effects can occur without explicit self-negating residue policy, which may mean ecology, dose, arousal, vulnerability, and interpretation explain more than the proposed residue axis."
reviews/originality/2026-05-26-operational-remainder-ecology-39a96b7ef7849b21.json:47:      "test_surface": "Retreat adverse-event datasets, Cheetah House style case intake data, and prospective Lumenary practice-seed safety tracking.",
