reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-the-deepest-unresolved-crux-is-whether-authority-transfer-is-the-right-m.json:187:        "G. Victor Sogen Hori, Koan and Kensho in the Rinzai Zen Curriculum: https://docslib.org/doc/1302437/the-koan-is-said-to-pose-to-the-ze-n-practitione-r-a-parado-x-unsolvabl-e-by-the-rational-intellectualizing-mind",
reviews/dialogues/2026-05-26-the-deepest-unresolved-crux-is-whether-authority-transfer-is-the-right-m.json:188:        "Shinran, Tannisho: https://jodoshinshu.faith/tannisho-a-record-in-lament-of-divergences/",
